author: National Geographic
description:
Aaron Pierre and Jayme Lawson had big shoes to fill when honoring the legacies of Malcolm X and Betty Shabazz, but having each other’s support and understanding throughout the process carried them to new heights. 

Watch the first episode of Genius: MLK/X on the Nat Geo YouTube channel.
title: Aaron Pierre and Jayme Lawson carried each other to new heights in #GeniusMLKX
